data.description: Needing a nice beautiful, updated vintage home? This 2-bedroom one bathroom has a large country kitchen with all updated appliances and fixtures. It offers you a laundry room with a storage area. Beautiful pine flooring throughout home. The bathroom has been updated with shower and sink. It gives you a front porch and a screened porch great for relaxing and enjoy the outdoors. Great location. Only minutes from Villa Rica and I-20.
